name: E-Commerce-Customer-Model-Preparation-Segmentation
description: E-Commerce Customer Segmentation focuses on analyzing transactional data from a UK-based online retailer to improve marketing strategies and boost sales. By applying clustering and classification techniques, we segment customers into distinct groups to understand their profiles and preferences. The code provides the steps for model preparation.

name: Sequential-Clustering-Algorithms
description: Implementing Sequential Clustering Algorithms (BSAS and MBSAS) from scratch

name: BTC-premia
description: We examine the risk premia of Bitcoin and compare with traditional equity. Moreover we explore different regimes based on nonparametric methods and display different state behaviours.

name: BSAS-Algorithm
description: Implementing BSAS (Basic Sequential Algorithmic Scheme) From Scratch

name: ML-Powered-Customer-Segmentation
description: A machine learning application built using CustomTkinter (CTk), designed to provide a user-friendly interface for customer segmentation through clustering techniques.
